headline: The Estée Lauder Companies Partners with Adobe to Scale the Production of Digital Marketing with Firefly Generative AI
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif. & NEW YORK, March 12, 2025--Today, Adobe (Nasdaq:ADBE) announced a partnership with The Estée Lauder Companies (NYSE:EL) (ELC) where the company is adopting Adobe Firefly and redefining its process of launching digital marketing campaigns through generative AI.
